	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quamvis vix mihi sint manus sufficientes, quibus ad te scribam, ita totus lavando undique ebullientibus pustulis squalleo, nolui tamen hunc sine meis ad te dimittere, ut videas plus mihi esse voluntatis quam facultatis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri redditae sunt mihi tuae 3. Mai datae, quibus scribis primo de <persName ref="p8437" cert="high">Erasmo Fabritio</persName> hic decumbente.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Misi ad illum matris suae literas percontatus simul de eius valetudine, quam non admodum male habere intelligo.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Promisit se ipsum matri velle scribere; quodsi videro aliquam exigere necessitatem, non ei deero etiam pecuniis, id quod matri meo nomine promittas velim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hodie perferuntur ad me literae admodum prolixae D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7201" cert="high">Jacobi Zorn</persName>, parochi aliquando <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1731">Regenstorffensis</placeName>; cupit hic etiam apud nostros promoveri, praetendit nescio quas suae reiectionis causas, quibus ego parum fido, nisi ex te prius intellexero, quomodo res illius habeant; sunt enim mihi ignotae.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Poteris ergo me certiorem reddere; eo usque enim nihil illi respondebo, donec ex te sciam, qualis sit aut quid illi credendum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Min herren baid schultheß <persName ref="p2305" cert="high">Nägeli</persName> und <persName type="auto_name">seckelmeister Haller</persName> sind gen <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Sollothurn</placeName>, doch niener umb anders dann abschlegig antwurt zuͦ geben.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gester sagt mir fenner <persName type="auto_name">imm Hag</persName>, Uri sye nitt da; wellinds gar abschlahen, haltind auch anderen Orten an, das si nitt darin gangind; in <placeName ref="l791" cert="high">Wallis</placeName> habinds fünff zenden auch abgschlagen, allein zwen bewilliget.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Graf von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2673" cert="high">Gryers</placeName> habe auch den sinen bi kopfabhawen verbotten, das sin nemand dencke; doch habind die von <placeName type="auto_name">Sanen</placeName> etwas bottschaffts zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Solloturn</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">In <placeName ref="l301" cert="high">Franckrych</placeName>, schript mir <persName ref="p3429" cert="high">Viretus</persName>, wüte die persequutio über dmaß; sye kein end.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucer</persName> und <persName ref="p4744" cert="high">Fagius</persName> sind in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Engelland</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So vil diß mal.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott sye mitt üch und den üweren allen; die gruͤßend von mir und allem minem volk.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Üch gruͤßt wider her fenner <persName type="auto_name">im Hag</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41" cert="high">Bern</placeName> 13. Mai 1549.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus, quem nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fidelissimo domino nostri Iesu Christi servo D. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino suo observando.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
